1. *Bih* se razveselio da Ä‡u te sresti. (I would be glad to meet you.)
2. *Bih* li mogao da ti pomognem? (Would I be able to help you?)
3. *Bila* bih ti vrlo zahvalna. (I would be very thankful to you.)
